data.description: Welcome to Phase One of Gendreau Estates, one of Dartmouth's sought-after neighborhoods built by Lou Franchi. Built in 2019, this custom home offers all the luxuries of new construction without the wait! The main living area boasts an open floor plan, modern kitchen with quartz counter tops, hardwood floors, ten foot ceilings, laundry and an office. Hardwood floors continue to the hallway and primary suite on the second floor and is accompanied by 3 additional bedrooms and full hall bath.Step into modern living at its best with this upgraded gem! Embrace eco-friendliness with owner-owned solar and a Tesla charger in the garage.  Imagine the convenience of a finished basement with in-law potential for guests or extended family. Step outside to your stamped concrete patio – an ideal spot for entertaining, accompanied by a handy storage shed and an extended driveway. Plus, your lush lawn stays vibrant thanks to the 12 zone irrigation system.
